Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.list

Class ItemListServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.base.AbstractComponentService<ItemListComponentType,ItemList>
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.list.ItemListServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ItemListService, Insertion
public class ItemListServiceImpl extends AbstractComponentService<ItemListComponentType,ItemList> implements ItemListService
Implementation of the ItemListService interface providing operations for selecting, deselecting, verifying, and retrieving items in a list-based component. Extends AbstractComponentService to manage creation and retrieval of ItemList instances.
